$BR
\[ 
\sin($a x)\cos($b x) = \frac{1}{2}(\sin (A x) + \sin(B x) )
\]
If \(A < B\), then:
$PAR
\(A\) = \{ans_rule(10) \}
$PAR
\(B\) = \{ans_rule(10) \}
END_TEXT

